y gadget, a popular\ntechnique for adding finality to longest-chain protocols.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 26 Oct 2020 16:53:28 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Apr 2021 06:22:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-04-05"}
