unter (quasi-)Parker, (quasi-)interchange,\ncurrent-driven and Kelvin-Helmholtz instabilities, as well as non-ideal\nquasi-modes, resistive tearing modes, up to magneto-thermal instabilities. The\nuse of high resolution sheds new light on previously calculated spectra,\nrevealing interesting spectral regions that have yet to be investigated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 27 Oct 2020 09:14:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Jun 2021 07:46:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-02"}
